Wales v Argentina, Saturday 12 November, Principality Stadium, 17.30 GMT
Wales v Japan, Saturday 19 November, Principality Stadium, 14.30 GMT
Wales v South Africa, Saturday 26 November, Principality Stadium, 17.30 GMT
